# Diagnostic screenshots and other images that get dropped into dev-notes/
# during a session — kept on disk for local reference, but not tracked. If
# you want a particular image preserved as project memory, force-add it
# with `git add -f dev-notes/<name>.png` and it'll stick.
dev-notes/*.png
dev-notes/*.jpg
dev-notes/*.jpeg
dev-notes/*.gif
dev-notes/*.webp
